Jean Gillie https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean_Gillie 0 Jean Gillie (14 October 1915 – 19 February 1949) was an English film actress of the 1930s and 1940s. Gillie appeared in 20 British and two American films before her career was cut short by her early death.
